### Quiz Question - Delete Question by ID
DELETE {{API_HostAddress}}/questions/{{questionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{instructor_token}}
Accept: application/json

### Quiz Attempt - Start Quiz Attempt
POST {{API_HostAddress}}/quizzes/{{quizId}}/attempts/start
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}
Accept: application/json

### Quiz Attempt - Submit Quiz Attempt
@attemptId = 123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000
POST {{API_HostAddress}}/quizzes/attempts/{{attemptId}}/submit
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "answers": [
        {
            "questionId": "d4c3b2a1-0987-6543",
            "selectedOptionIds": ["optionIdForParis"]
        }
    ]
}

### Quiz Attempt - Get Quiz Attempt Result
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/quizzes/attempts/{{attemptId}}/result
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}
Accept: application/json

### Quiz Attempt - Get My Quiz Attempts for a Quiz
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/quizzes/{{quizId}}/attempts/my-attempts
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}
Accept: application/json
